  "detailed_description": "<strong>WELCOME TO MEANDERS!</strong><br>A sparkling theme park full of platform and environmental puzzles. <strong>Have fun!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734920/extras/e57ed56f4727cad9cb1d8573dd2b8f09.poster.avif?t=1569935305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734920/extras/e57ed56f4727cad9cb1d8573dd2b8f09.webm?t=1569935305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734920/extras/e57ed56f4727cad9cb1d8573dd2b8f09.mp4?t=1569935305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 levels of instant play with no loading times: relax or speedrun to the exit!<br></li><li>Jump, bounce, slide, teleport! Cannons too are a totally safe mean of transportation<br></li><li>Enjoy the company of an all-powerful AI god - <span class=\"bb_spoiler\">Unless you find out how to destroy it</span><br></li><li>Speedrun Mode & Steam Leaderboards available!<br></li><li>Original Soundtrack both funky and soothing<br></li><li>Use the ATOMIC STUFF to activate the insane game and visual modes!!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>WELCOME TO MEANDERS!</strong><br>A sparkling theme park full of platform and environmental puzzles. <strong>Have fun!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734920/extras/e57ed56f4727cad9cb1d8573dd2b8f09.poster.avif?t=1569935305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734920/extras/e57ed56f4727cad9cb1d8573dd2b8f09.webm?t=1569935305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734920/extras/e57ed56f4727cad9cb1d8573dd2b8f09.mp4?t=1569935305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 levels of instant play with no loading times: relax or speedrun to the exit!<br></li><li>Jump, bounce, slide, teleport! Cannons too are a totally safe mean of transportation<br></li><li>Enjoy the company of an all-powerful AI god - <span class=\"bb_spoiler\">Unless you find out how to destroy it</span><br></li><li>Speedrun Mode & Steam Leaderboards available!<br></li><li>Original Soundtrack both funky and soothing<br></li><li>Use the ATOMIC STUFF to activate the insane game and visual modes!!</li></ul>",
